<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-690] log4j-web pom.xml - test artifacts should be in test scope</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-690</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, log4j-web includes junit, spring-test and easymock are present as test dependencies. Unfortunately these dependencies are propagated to the outside. So please add &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;test&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt; to all test dependencies like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;junit&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;junit&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;test&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.springframework&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;spring-test&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;test&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.easymock&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;easymock&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;test&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Philip&lt;/p&gt;</description>
